metadata.name: [ ANOMALY: LQ.004 ]
metadata.description:
L: Solar System, Moon
D: 16 JUL 1969
(NASA. Apollo 11 mission data)

>// Object description:
It is a morphing liquid metal substance with an anti-gravity field. Transfer mental waves that cause conciseness disorders. Affected astronauts report the exact image of the face, calling them. After the loss of several crew members object decided to be distracted.
>// Status: ELIMINATED
